{"tid":1207502,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[邏輯L] 小弟發現一個好嚴重嘅問題","createTime":"2019-06-12T06:44:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T07:24:48.000Z","uid":258784,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1cf688a17defb0bc036c313e42b62306cb579158","tid":1207502,"uid":258784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:44:16.000Z","msg":"因為大家都係熱愛自由<br />\n              &darr;&darr;<br />\n    各自有各自想法<br />\n              &darr;&darr;<br />\n    冇人代表到我地<br />\n              &darr;&darr;<br />\n組織鬆散，行動不一致<br />\n              &darr;&darr;<br />\n 烏合之眾，政府唔驚<br />\n              &darr;&darr;<br />\n    失敗收場？？？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反之，如果我地有一個或者一啲發師號令嘅人，大家行動一置，例如：今日6點唔撤回，就癱瘓港鐵；今晩12點前唔撤回就佔領機場。<br />\n咁先可以有效分配人手，唔會俾佢地拖死。<br />\n<br />\n以上為小弟之愚見，大家討論下～～"},{"pid":"d11fe826e5d4c52f9c89c3d71efe93319f91e678","tid":1207502,"uid":16061,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:47:55.000Z","msg":"擒王"},{"pid":"ba4b40e489196b0d9ad27ec5e4d2510ebc6a7ef1","tid":1207502,"uid":258784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:54:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe15c0876de2320a1a3234b744610def3abe9d59","tid":1207502,"uid":28818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:58:27.000Z","msg":"[文宣組求散播] 聲明<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1207438\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1207438</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7632589f61faf247fb53854a7d902e847dd5839e","tid":1207502,"uid":48796,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T07:04:27.000Z","msg":"有大台 =&gt; 俾人騎劫<br />\n冇大台 =&gt; 冇人指揮<br />\n<br />\n分小隊, 默契, 唔好內訌"},{"pid":"36b17ca4425117478b1114cdfc895024fc82a3d3","tid":1207502,"uid":258784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7632589f61faf247fb53854a7d902e847dd5839e","tid":1207502,"uid":48796,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T07:04:27.000Z","msg":"有大台 =&gt; 俾人騎劫<br />\n冇大台 =&gt; 冇人指揮<br />\n<br />\n